{
  "productId": "id-product-nya",
  "quantity": 2
}

###Get Cart
GET https://bubbly-connection-production-1305.up.railway.app/api/cart
Authorization: token-user...

###Checkout
POST https://bubbly-connection-production-1305.up.railway.app/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-user...

{
  "addressId": "id-address-nya"
}

###Get My Orders
GET https://bubbly-connection-production-1305.up.railway.app/api/orders
Authorization: token-user...

###Create Payment
POST https://bubbly-connection-production-1305.up.railway.app/api/payments/id-order-nya
Authorization: token-user...

###Get All Orders (Admin)
GET https://bubbly-connection-production-1305.up.railway.app/api/orders/admin?page=1&size=10
Authorization: token-admin...

###Update Order Status (Admin)
PATCH https://bubbly-connection-production-1305.up.railway.app/api/orders/admin/id-order-nya/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-admin...

{
  "status": "PAID"
}